author: fdmanana
msg: Bug fix: the separator for media types in the 'Accept' header is a comma. The semicolon separates a media type from its	parameters.
A more complete	solution, which	takes into account Q values, was submitted upstream: https://github.com/mochi/mochiweb/issues/issue/21.
